{"tid":2344184,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「撥亂反正」TVB:我地已經贏咗！黃絲：唉！我地又輸民意！","createTime":"2020-12-28T13:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T11:46:49.000Z","uid":219635,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8c1900ca1546f0c78bc12cdf421e958e2ccdb1","tid":2344184,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"ViuTV的真人騷《全民造星III》掀起全城熱話，更迫使TVB有樣學樣急推航空業才藝比賽《衝上雲霄大選》硬撼。據《蘋果》了解《造星III》總決賽當晚，<span class=\"red\">ViuTV平均收視有6.5點，即約43萬觀眾捧場，最高有7.5點，有大約49萬觀眾，至於TVB《衝上雲霄》平均收視15點（約98萬觀眾），而最高為17點，有111萬觀眾捧場。</span>不過大台現時的收視已改為統計跨平台收視，包括傳統模擬頻道、數碼頻頻、及大台app直播，15點平均收視或者充滿水分。<br />\n<br />\n據悉《造星III》總決賽比起前一星期同時段節目升了1.9點，多出約12萬觀眾，至於大台《衝上雲霄》比對前一星期升了2點，多了13萬觀眾，疫情下人人留家抗疫，對整體電視台收視有提升。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">估唔到又輸民意！咩都輸哂！呢鋪仲點夠膽認自己深黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201228/PFF3BD4F25AM7HQICXRTPN6BIY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3zdNv9fBjUTm6P1uW8K2hbq7Hjo2aqeJcCE9PFO-4LPZHzwr7tfN2HhGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201228%2FPFF3BD4F25AM7HQICXRTPN6BIY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3zdNv9fBjUTm6P1uW8K2hbq7Hjo2aqeJcCE9PFO-4LPZHzwr7tfN2HhGI&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=5e7749ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201228%2FPFF3BD4F25AM7HQICXRTPN6BIY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3zdNv9fBjUTm6P1uW8K2hbq7Hjo2aqeJcCE9PFO-4LPZHzwr7tfN2HhGI&h=92a0353a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201228/PFF3BD4F25AM7HQICXRTPN6BIY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3zdNv9fBjUTm6P1uW8K2hbq7Hjo2aqeJcCE9PFO-4LPZHzwr7tfN2HhGI</a><br />\n一定有手足支持左TVB!一定係造假！假新聞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fe559606a615a3a026441cadc2fd4ebbb809c3","tid":2344184,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足去哂邊？"},{"pid":"dcde3cb803bf72d8c81ed40b766e67509eb2b928","tid":2344184,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9125a54307a48ddbaffc81cb6699379da7136060","tid":2344184,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1169747e8ca7616c41eec63f82f03860881d15bf","tid":2344184,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab22e79a3a745514e9290fe645bf464d352de5ee","tid":2344184,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset